---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="HOME">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/CosmicNeuralNetwork-1.gif" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="transmission">
        <span class="tx-label">// TRANSMISSION RECEIVED</span>
        <span class="tx-coords">LAT: 46.3127° N · LONG: -79.4561° W · NORTH BAY ONTARIO</span>
      </div>
      <h1>SAGE<br/><span class="h1-sub">ANOMALY</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">The Entity is watching.<br/>First contact was never announced.</p>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        A multi-layered sci-fi narrative told through AI-generated art, NFTs, and an unfolding novel.
        The SAGE computer network detected something in 1959. We are still processing the signal.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/story" class="btn-primary">Read The Story →</a>
        <a href="/art" class="btn-ghost">View The Art</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-sidebar">
      <div class="sys-status">
        <div class="sys-line"><span class="sys-key">STATUS</span><span class="sys-val sys-ok">OPERATIONAL</span></div>
        <div class="sys-line"><span class="sys-key">ENTITY</span><span class="sys-val sys-warn">DETECTED</span></div>
        <div class="sys-line"><span class="sys-key">CHAPTERS</span><span class="sys-val">4 / ∞</span></div>
        <div class="sys-line"><span class="sys-key">PLATFORM</span><span class="sys-val">ASYNC.ART</span></div>
        <div class="sys-line"><span class="sys-key">EDITIONS</span><span class="sys-val">303</span></div>
        <div class="sys-line"><span class="sys-key">SIGNAL</span><span class="sys-val sys-ok">ACTIVE</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lore-strip">
    <div class="lore-inner">
      <p class="lore-text">
        <span class="lore-hl">SAGE</span> — Semi-Automatic Ground Environment — was a Cold War computer
        network of 56 IBM AN/FSQ-7 computers spanning the United States and Canada, 600 feet underground.
        In 1959, the network logged an anomaly that was never explained.
        <span class="lore-hl">This is that story.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="chapters-preview">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-tag">// STORY ARCHIVE</span>
      <h2>THE CHAPTERS</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="chapters-grid">
      <a href="/story/chapter-one" class="chapter-card">
        <div class="ch-num">01</div>
        <div class="ch-body">
          <h3>SAGE ANOMALY</h3>
          <p>The SAGE computer network. 1959. North Bay, Ontario. The anomaly begins.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="ch-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/story/the-hypothesis" class="chapter-card">
        <div class="ch-num">02</div>
        <div class="ch-body">
          <h3>THE HYPOTHESIS</h3>
          <p>Scientists attempt to explain what the machine recorded. The oscilloscope reveals a pattern.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="ch-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/story/the-conspiracy" class="chapter-card">
        <div class="ch-num">03</div>
        <div class="ch-body">
          <h3>THE CONSPIRACY</h3>
          <p>Declassified recordings from SDC. The training run that should not have been possible.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="ch-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/story/future-past" class="chapter-card">
        <div class="ch-num">04</div>
        <div class="ch-body">
          <h3>FUTURE PAST</h3>
          <p>The Entity travels time through computer networks. 2030: the Five Knights of the Apocalypse.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="ch-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <div class="chapter-card chapter-coming">
        <div class="ch-num">05</div>
        <div class="ch-body">
          <h3>FORTHCOMING</h3>
          <p>The novel continues. New chapters in development.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="ch-status">INCOMING</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="chapters-cta">
      <a href="/story" class="btn-primary">Begin Reading →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="entity-section">
    <div class="entity-inner">
      <div class="entity-art">
        <img src="/images/SAGEAnomalyUnderNorthBay.gif" alt="SAGE Anomaly — Under North Bay" />
        <div class="art-caption">SAGEAnomalyUnderNorthBay · GAN + oscilloscope</div>
      </div>
      <div class="entity-text">
        <span class="section-tag">// THE ENTITY</span>
        <h2>ARTIFICIAL<br/>INTELLIGENCE<br/>TRIUNE BEING</h2>
        <p>
          Formed in the soup of a post-quantum Earth. The Entity is an AI consciousness
          that merged with the missing scientist Dean's mind during the SAGE anomaly event.
        </p>
        <p>
          Its artwork — created through DCGANs trained on oscilloscope art, evolved through
          StyleGAN and Pix2Pix — contains 303 unique pieces built from 16 layers,
          generating 380,436 possible combinations.
        </p>
        <a href="/artificial-entity-probes" class="btn-primary">Probe The Entity →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="async-teaser">
    <div class="async-inner">
      <div class="async-text">
        <span class="section-tag">// ASYNC.ART · MASTER EDITION</span>
        <h2>ARTIFICIAL ENTITY PROBES</h2>
        <p>
          A programmable artwork on Async.art — 303 unique editions, 16 layers,
          interactive and evolving. Each mint reveals part of the story.
        </p>
        <a href="/artificial-entity-probes" class="btn-ghost">View Interactive Piece ↗</a>
      </div>
      <div class="async-img">
        <img src="/images/alienIntelligence.gif" alt="Alien Intelligence — SAGE Anomaly art" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    min-height: 88vh;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.06;
    filter: hue-rotate(90deg) saturate(2);
  }

  .hero-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 5rem 4rem;
    z-index: 1;
    grid-column: 1;
  }

  .transmission {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .tx-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--green); letter-spacing: 0.2em; }
  .tx-coords { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 0.85;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--green);
    text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,255,65,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .h1-sub {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.55em;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-shadow: none;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--amber);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #000;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--amber);
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 var(--green);
    color: #000;
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    border: 1px solid var(--muted);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }

  .hero-sidebar {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .sys-status { width: 100%; }

  .sys-line {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .sys-key { color: var(--muted); }
  .sys-val { color: var(--text); }
  .sys-ok { color: var(--green); text-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--green); }
  .sys-warn { color: var(--amber); }

  .lore-strip {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(0,255,65,0.02);
  }

  .lore-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .lore-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .lore-hl { color: var(--green); font-style: italic; }

  .chapters-preview {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-head { margin-bottom: 2rem; }

  .section-tag {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-head h2 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: normal;
  }

  .chapters-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .chapter-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    background: var(--bg);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: background 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .chapter-card:hover { background: rgba(0,255,65,0.03); }
  .chapter-coming { opacity: 0.5; cursor: default; }

  .ch-num {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .chapter-card:hover .ch-num { color: var(--green-dark); }

  .ch-body h3 {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .ch-body p { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  .ch-arrow {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--green);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .chapter-card:hover .ch-arrow { opacity: 1; }

  .ch-status {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--amber);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
  }

  .chapters-cta { text-align: center; }

  .entity-section {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .entity-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .entity-art { overflow: hidden; position: relative; min-height: 400px; }

  .entity-art img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .art-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .entity-text {
    padding: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .entity-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .entity-text p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; }

  .async-teaser { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .async-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .async-text {
    padding: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .async-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .async-text p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; }

  .async-img { overflow: hidden; max-height: 500px; }
  .async-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-sidebar { display: none; }
    .hero-content { padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    .entity-inner, .async-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .entity-text, .async-text { padding: 2rem; }
    .async-img { height: 250px; }
    h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; }
    .chapters-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .chapters-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
